{"service_name": "Cyber Security Services - Policy and Standards", "service_id": "7395715778471676", "company_name": "Amethyst Risk Management Limited", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Amethyst Risk Management Limited\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Cyber Security Services - Policy and Standards\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Provision of support, guidance and advice to the public and private sectors to ensure alignment and compliance with cyber security and Information Assurance (IA) policies and standards, including the Security Policy Framework (SPF), CESG Information Assurance Portfolio (IAP), Nuclear Regulations and ISO27001.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Alignment with the requirements of the Cloud Security Principles.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Alignment to international standards such as ISO 27001, PCI-DSS.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Alignment to government and CESG policies and standards.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Review of existing IA and cyber policies and procedures.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Producing compliant IA and cyber strategies, policies and procedures.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Providing IA compliance advice to inform decision making\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Providing staff awareness briefing and training.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Gap analysis for achievement of ISO 27001 certification.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Producing business continuity plans and risk management strategies.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Compliance with legal requirements (e.g. DPA, CMA, FOI Acts).\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Service delivered by experienced IA and cyber security specialists.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Advice and guidance compliant with latest government cyber policy.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Policies and procedures tailored to the organisation\u2019s needs.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Production of comprehensive policy, standards and procedures documentation.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Improved understanding of information security policies and standards.\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Improved IA and cyber security awareness for the organisation.\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3795 to \u00a31188 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Other\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92200/7395715778471676-pricing-document-2015-10-02-1518.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92200/7395715778471676-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-02-1518.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmar